KMSCL is hiring Company Secretary in Trivandrum

<strong>Qualification and Experience:</strong>

1. Candidate should have passed Company Secretary Professional Examination and acquired Associate Membership of Institute of Company Secretaries of India;
2. Minimum 2 years post qualification experience, as on 25.07.2018, in Public / Private Sector Companies;
3. Bachelor Degree in Law will be a desirable qualification.

<strong>Remuneration:</strong>

Consolidated Pay of `25,000/- per month.

<strong>Application:</strong>

Eligible candidates may send their duly filled in Application Form, through email, along with scanned copies of relevant documents to prove Age, Qualifications etc. to or submit through Speed Post / Courier so as to reach the above address, on or before 8th August 2018.

Application Form can be downloaded from the website of the Corporation (<a href="http://www.kmscl.kerala.gov.in">www.kmscl.kerala.gov.in</a>).

